project_descr: Strengthening the Marine and Coastal Protected Areas of Russia

outputs.output_descr:
The project objective is to facilitate expansion of the national system of marine and coastal protected areas and improve its management effectiveness as reflected in design issues relating to both individual sites and protected area systems and adequacy and appropriateness of management systems and processes, and the delivery of protected area objectives.
